---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Sobre Nosotros - Bytech Paraguay">
    <main class="bg-black">
<div class="lg:container lg:mx-auto lg:py-16 md:py-12 md:px-6 py-12 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-center dark:text-white lg:text-4xl text-3xl lg:leading-9 leading-7 text-gray-800 font-semibold">FAQ's</h1>


    <div class="lg:w-8/12 w-full mx-auto">
        <hr class="w-full lg:mt-10 md:mt-12 md:mb-8 my-8" />

        <div class="w-full md:px-6">
            <div id="mainHeading" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full">
                <div class="">
                    <p class="flex justify-center items-center font-medium text-base leading-6 md:leading-4 text-gray-100"><span class="lg:mr-6 mr-4 text-white lg:text-2xl md:text-xl text-lg leading-6 md:leading-5 lg:leading-4 font-semibold ">1.</span> Donde estan ubicados?</p>
                </div>
                <button aria-label="toggler" class="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-800" data-menu>
                    <img class="transform dark:hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2.svg" alt="toggler">
                    <img class="transform dark:block hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2dark.svg" alt="toggler">
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="menu" class="hidden mt-6 w-full">
                <p class="text-base leading-6 text-gray-100  font-normal">
                    Estamos ubicados en San Lorenzo, Paraguay. Actualmente no contamos con tienda fisica pero se pueden realizar las negociaciones en persona.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

     <hr class="w-full lg:mt-10 my-8" />

        <div class="w-full md:px-6">
            <div id="mainHeading" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full">
                <div class="">
                    <p class="flex justify-center items-center  font-medium text-base leading-6 lg:leading-4 text-gray-100"><span class="lg:mr-6 text-white mr-4 lg:text-2xl md:text-xl text-lg leading-6 md:leading-5 lg:leading-4 font-semibold ">2.</span> Tienen Garantia?</p>
                </div>
                <button aria-label="toggler" class="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-800" data-menu>
                    <img class="transform dark:hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2.svg" alt="toggler">
                    <img class="transform dark:block hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2dark.svg" alt="toggler">
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="menu" class="hidden mt-6 w-full">
                <p class="text-base leading-6 text-gray-100  font-normal">
                    Si tenemos, nuestros servicios y productos cuentan con garantia, incluso se pueden realizar contratos para asegurar un buen servicio cumpliendo los requerimientos del acuerdo.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="w-full lg:mt-10 my-8" />

        <div class="w-full md:px-6">
            <div id="mainHeading" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full">
                <div class="">
                    <p class="flex justify-center items-center text-white font-medium text-base leading-6 lg:leading-4"><span class="lg:mr-6  mr-4 lg:text-2xl md:text-xl text-lg leading-6 md:leading-5 lg:leading-4 font-semibold text-gray-100">3.</span>Sus servicios son solo a empresas?</p>
                </div>
                <button aria-label="toggler" class="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-800" data-menu>
                    <img class="transform dark:hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2.svg" alt="toggler">
                    <img class="transform dark:block hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2dark.svg" alt="toggler">
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="menu" class="hidden mt-6 w-full">
                <p class="text-base leading-6 text-gray-100 dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
                    Realizamos servicios a todos, aunque nos enfocamos en empresas tambien trabajamos con emprendimientos y proyectos personales.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="w-full lg:mt-10 my-8" />

        <div class="w-full md:px-6">
            <div id="mainHeading" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full">
                <div class="">
                    <p class="flex justify-center items-center dark:text-white font-medium text-base leading-6 lg:leading-4 text-gray-800"><span class="lg:mr-6 dark:text-white mr-4 lg:text-2xl md:text-xl text-lg leading-6 md:leading-5 lg:leading-4 font-semibold text-gray-800">4.</span>Realizan cobros en cuotas?</p>
                </div>
                <button aria-label="toggler" class="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-800" data-menu>
                    <img class="transform dark:hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2.svg" alt="toggler">
                    <img class="transform dark:block hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2dark.svg" alt="toggler">
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="menu" class="hidden mt-6 w-full">
                <p class="text-base leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
                    Dependiendo del servicio y del costo, se realizan cobros a cuotas en algunos casos.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="w-full lg:mt-10 my-8" />

        <div class="w-full md:px-6">
            <div id="mainHeading" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full">
                <div class="">
                    <p class="flex justify-center items-center dark:text-white font-medium text-base leading-6 lg:leading-4 text-gray-800"><span class="lg:mr-6 dark:text-white mr-4 lg:text-2xl md:text-xl text-lg leading-6 md:leading-5 lg:leading-4 font-semibold text-gray-800">5.</span>Con que tecnologias trabajan?</p>
                </div>
                <button aria-label="toggler" class="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-800" data-menu>
                    <img class="transform dark:hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2.svg" alt="toggler">
                    <img class="transform dark:block hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2dark.svg" alt="toggler">
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="menu" class="hidden mt-6 w-full">
                <p class="text-base leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
                    Dependiendo del proyecto, trabajamos con codigo Javascript, PHP y varios Frameworks. Aunque en algunos casos trabajamos con Wordpress y Woocomerce.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="w-full lg:mt-10 my-8" />

        <div class="w-full md:px-6">
            <div id="mainHeading" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full">
                <div class="">
                    <p class="flex justify-center items-center dark:text-white font-medium text-base leading-6 lg:leading-4 text-gray-800"><span class="lg:mr-6 dark:text-white mr-4 lg:text-2xl md:text-xl text-lg leading-6 md:leading-5 lg:leading-4 font-semibold text-gray-800">6.</span>Que herramientas de dise√±o utilizan?</p>
                </div>
                <button aria-label="toggler" class="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-800" data-menu>
                    <img class="transform dark:hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2.svg" alt="toggler">
                    <img class="transform dark:block hidden " src="https://tuk-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/can-uploader/faq-8-svg2dark.svg" alt="toggler">
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="menu" class="hidden mt-6 w-full">
                <p class="text-base leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
                    Utilizamos Coreldraw, Adobe illustrator y Photoshop, aunque en proyectos mas basicos usamos Canva y Microsoft Designer.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="w-full lg:mt-10 my-8" />
    </div>
</div>
</main>
<script>
let elements = document.querySelectorAll("[data-menu]");
for (let i = 0; i < elements.length; i++) {
let main = elements[i];

main.addEventListener("click", function () {
let element = main.parentElement?.parentElement;
let indicators = main.querySelectorAll("img");
let child = element?.querySelector("#menu");
let h = element?.querySelector("#mainHeading>div>p");

h?.classList.toggle("font-semibold");
child?.classList.toggle("hidden");
indicators[0].classList.toggle("rotate-180");
});
}
    </script>
</Layout>